{"tid":1330863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果A1: 60港青年 赴台求庇護","createTime":"2019-07-18T17:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T15:25:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":278,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"b9859899721fd6dc3c4af6685da3dcbc62b6de0e","tid":1330863,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67501210_10157855141457448_6226327592664825856_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_oc=AQmu79_db-FbjsfK_q7L9pS1afgiWQ-viuJqNoDo0iTECZYeWifEcxoxWm0GRqDpqZc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=f0abcbaba38e35259f972da3e9945064&amp;oe=5DBC7F5C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67501210_10157855141457448_6226327592664825856_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_oc%3DAQmu79_db-FbjsfK_q7L9pS1afgiWQ-viuJqNoDo0iTECZYeWifEcxoxWm0GRqDpqZc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Df0abcbaba38e35259f972da3e9945064%26oe%3D5DBC7F5C&h=342c5ff5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb41a11fb8b129c4e05bb14fc06b557467d4df9e","tid":1330863,"uid":240362,"like":179,"dislike":2,"score":177,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:24:26.000Z","msg":"【A1頭條】特首林鄭月娥拒絕回應民間五大訴求，包括承諾不檢控示威者，終於引爆第一波青少年「逃亡潮」。本報獲悉，示威者7月1日衝擊立法會後，其中30人已飛抵台灣「暫避」，並尋求庇護；另有約30名示威者亦準備逃亡到台灣。據悉，協助的中間人已跟台灣陸委會接觸尋求庇護，並獲開出「逗留條件」，現階段料將參考「林榮基方案」，讓各人不斷延長居留台灣。"},{"pid":"9e19f74aa594d867ee5541d783f985fca406ff74","tid":1330863,"uid":24615,"like":286,"dislike":2,"score":284,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"...去台灣,真係唔驚korea fish.一年後又要著草"},{"pid":"3c5d27059953d0422ef68d83f224747c3d12fb34","tid":1330863,"uid":103230,"like":193,"dislike":1,"score":192,"quote":{"pid":"9e19f74aa594d867ee5541d783f985fca406ff74","tid":1330863,"uid":24615,"like":286,"dislike":2,"score":284,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"...去台灣,真係唔驚korea fish.一年後又要著草"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:42:03.000Z","msg":"綠營實搵佢地幫手宣傳香港點俾老玩殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6bb85c87f3c60ec49593921b9cc4f08eec02e4","tid":1330863,"uid":31788,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"quote":{"pid":"3c5d27059953d0422ef68d83f224747c3d12fb34","tid":1330863,"uid":103230,"like":193,"dislike":1,"score":192,"quote":{"pid":"9e19f74aa594d867ee5541d783f985fca406ff74","tid":1330863,"uid":24615,"like":286,"dislike":2,"score":284,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"...去台灣,真係唔驚korea fish.一年後又要著草"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:42:03.000Z","msg":"綠營實搵佢地幫手宣傳香港點俾老玩殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:43:35.000Z","msg":"係⋯咁多人過去幫手講實有個優勢喺度"},{"pid":"56c058874adafe0ff75405078ca9538749e896b5","tid":1330863,"uid":258696,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:44:25.000Z","msg":"UP"},{"pid":"59f6ef72d3baa5b3828b78dc55040cc569e3cb16","tid":1330863,"uid":128923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4950ad6635c83515deadb36088ccc8b09f0208","tid":1330863,"uid":17376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4addf317542e609a796acf91a17fe7eebec4a3","tid":1330863,"uid":69746,"like":269,"dislike":2,"score":267,"quote":{"pid":"9e19f74aa594d867ee5541d783f985fca406ff74","tid":1330863,"uid":24615,"like":286,"dislike":2,"score":284,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"...去台灣,真係唔驚korea fish.一年後又要著草"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:54:31.000Z","msg":"如果到時真係選左佢出黎 台灣人抵死啦 香港無撚得選就話啫 台灣人有一人一票都仲咁on9"},{"pid":"80189e04d183d45344b8d583c1caa8b2f31ae1ec","tid":1330863,"uid":167289,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:08:19.000Z","msg":"講出嚟做咩"},{"pid":"e0b217c96c32f7c3550565f27c63e2d748168c0e","tid":